 			var div=document.getElementById("skipser-youtubevid-"+id);
 			div.parentNode.replaceChild( iframe, div)
 	}
     </script>
     <script>
      function slideOut(){
 			$('.main-content').css('overflow', 'hidden');
 			$('.slideout-right').animate({left: Number($('.slideout-right').width()+40) + 'px'}, {queue:false, duration: 500});
 		}
 		function slideIn(){
 			$('.slideout-right').animate({left: 40 + 'px'}, {queue:false, duration: 500});
 		}
 		if($('.slideout-right')){
             $('.toggle-button').on('click', function(){
 				if($('.slideout-right').position().left > 40){
 					slideIn();
 				}else{
 	                slideOut();
 				}
             });
 			/*left: -68px;
     top: 29px;*/
 			$('.toggle-button').css('left',-1 * ($('.toggle-button').width()/2 + $('.toggle-button').height()/2 + $('.toggle-button').width()/15) + 'px');
 			$('.toggle-button').css('top', $('.toggle-button').width()/2 - 10 + 'px');
 			$('.toggle-button').css('display', 'inline-block');
 			setTimeout(function(){
 				slideOut();
 			}, 5000);
 		}
     </script>

      optimizeYouTubeEmbeds()
